{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T13:30:08.163Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"agent_message","message":"The aggregate output-token gap is almost entirely Zod, so I’m checking that transcript specifically rather than attributing it to Graph’s normal response format. The key distinction is that Claude’s “output tokens” include its hidden reasoning and tool-call generation, not Entire Graph’s returned context.","phase":"commentary","memory_citation":null}}
