ate conclusion is:\n\n- Entire Graph did not generally cause more output.\n- The tested Zod defect caused Claude to distrust the result, duplicate the investigation using file tools, and spend roughly 5,500 extra output tokens reasoning through the discrepancy.\n- The repaired Graph head should be evaluated with pre-indexing and without a forced redundant verification workflow. File tools should remain available naturally, but the agent should choose whether verification is needed.","started_at":1784381393,"completed_at":1784381451,"duration_ms":57391,"time_to_first_token_ms":14331}}
