{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T13:42:16.341Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"agent_message","message":"The repaired head now returns the complete Zod neighborhood from the prebuilt index in about 0.17 seconds. The same replay exposed one additional general Python bug: a `Path(\"-\")` example in a comment was being resolved as a real constructor. That is fixed and regression-tested; Click now returns only its six repository-authored callees, with imported calls clearly marked external. I’m publishing this product fix before changing the benchmark harness.","phase":"commentary","memory_citation":null}}
{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T13:42:16.341Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"message","id":"msg_0bd6d73b974b1fab016a5b82b83ce481919eda836a0c2d86ae","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"The repaired head now returns the complete Zod neighborhood from the prebuilt index in about 0.17 seconds. The same replay exposed one additional general Python bug: a `Path(\"-\")` example in a comment was being resolved as a real constructor. That is fixed and regression-tested; Click now returns only its six repository-authored callees, with imported calls clearly marked external. I’m publishing this product fix before changing the benchmark harness."}],"phase":"commentary","internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f756f-5147-7222-9084-187ed68d3651"}}}
