{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T13:46:21.391Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"agent_message","id":"amsg_019f757a-5d4f-7ec1-ba91-f8bc0861a78e","author":"/root/graph_audit","recipient":"/root","content":[{"type":"input_text","text":"Message Type: FINAL_ANSWER\nTask name: /root\nSender: /root/graph_audit\nPayload:\nAudit complete; no files changed by me.\n\n- PR #43 is clean, pushed at `99e7259`, open/ready/mergeable. Six checks pass; Windows test remains in progress.\n- Zod repair is correct: 7 callers, abstract `_parse`, authored `isAsync`, 14 paths.\n- Click’s false `Path` construction is fixed at `99e7259`. Remaining output includes 11 external callees.\n- Chi still includes 7 test callers alongside the single production caller.\n- Full search preindex currently does not warm neighbors because [`search.go`](/Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph/internal/sem/search.go:245) keys all selected files while [`neighbors.go`](/Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph/internal/cli/neighbors.go:99) uses `OnlyFiles=nil`.\n- Neighbor cache hits are unobservable because the hit boolean is discarded.\n- Agent output enumerates every Cartesian path in [`neighbors.go`](/Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph/internal/cli/neighbors.go:399), producing 48/14/68 redundant path lines for Chi/Zod/Click.\n- Zod search ranks the generated `deno/lib/types.ts` mirror before `src/types.ts`.\n\nRecommended pre-smoke minimum:\n\n1. Add a query-independent `index` command and let selective search probe/reuse its full-snapshot cache.\n2. Expose `index_cache_hit` and `index_latency_ms` in neighbor JSON.\n3. Render agent paths as one compact caller × focus × callee family.\n4. Add `--internal-only` and `--exclude-tests` response filters.\n5. Collapse semantic mirror duplicates in search, preferring the shortest canonical path.\n6. Preindex before the harness timer and assert both search and neighbors hit the same cache.\n\nFocused TypeScript and cache tests passed locally."}],"internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f756f-5147-7222-9084-187ed68d3651"}}}
