{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T13:55:29.422Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"agent_message","message":"The benchmark runner now has a fail-closed preflight: it builds and validates Graph/CBM indexes before any Claude process, records setup separately, rejects cache/profile/tree mismatches, accepts one appropriate product retrieval instead of forcing two, and rejects timed reindexing. Its full regression suite passes. I’m reviewing the parallel product patches together now before the next incremental commit.","phase":"commentary","memory_citation":null}}
{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T13:55:29.422Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"message","id":"msg_0bd6d73b974b1fab016a5b85d15fb8819182011e9f4e7fde4a","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"The benchmark runner now has a fail-closed preflight: it builds and validates Graph/CBM indexes before any Claude process, records setup separately, rejects cache/profile/tree mismatches, accepts one appropriate product retrieval instead of forcing two, and rejects timed reindexing. Its full regression suite passes. I’m reviewing the parallel product patches together now before the next incremental commit."}],"phase":"commentary","internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f756f-5147-7222-9084-187ed68d3651"}}}
