{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T14:30:37.812Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"custom_tool_call","id":"ctc_0bd6d73b974b1fab016a5b8e0dc1f4819197d59cb9c51af5c4","status":"completed","call_id":"call_lVg4ZnVFLbUPZkG8ZQaZ2GcK","name":"exec","input":"const patch = \"*** Begin Patch\\n*** Update File: /Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph/internal/cli/root.go\\n@@\\n-  entire graph index --repo . [--profile syntax-only|fast|full] [--cache-dir path] [--format json] [--head]\\n+  entire graph index --repo . [--profile syntax-only|fast|full] [--cache-dir path] [--format json] [--head] [--ignore-file path] [--include-file path]\\n*** Update File: /Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph/README.md\\n@@\\n ```sh\\n-entire graph search --repo . --query \\\"retry logic for webhook delivery\\\" --top-k 20 --format agent\\n+entire graph search --repo . --query \\\"retry logic for webhook delivery\\\" --top-k 20 --format agent --head --profile full --cache-dir /path/to/cache\\n ```\\n+\\n+That invocation reuses the prepared committed-tree index. Omit `--head` and\\n+the cache flags when the agent must inspect dirty working-tree edits instead.\\n*** End Patch\";\ntext(await tools.apply_patch(patch));\n","internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f756f-5147-7222-9084-187ed68d3651"}}}
{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T14:30:38.161Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"patch_apply_end","call_id":"exec-b96e767d-cded-487d-9080-7c97bf637482","turn_id":"019f756f-5147-7222-9084-187ed68d3651","stdout":"Success. Updated the following files:\nM /Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph/internal/cli/root.go\nM /Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph/README.md\n","stderr":"","success":true,"changes":{"/Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph/internal/cli/root.go":{"type":"update","unified_diff":"@@ -104,3 +104,3 @@\n   entire graph edges --repo . --format ndjson [--worktree] [--progress] [--ignore-file path] [--include-file path]\n-  entire graph index --repo . [--profile syntax-only|fast|full] [--cache-dir path] [--format json] [--head]\n+  entire graph index --repo . [--profile syntax-only|fast|full] [--cache-dir path] [--format json] [--head] [--ignore-file path] [--include-file path]\n   entire graph search --query \"issue or concept\" --repo . [--format json|ndjson|text|agent] [--top-k 20] [--max-context-bytes 16384] [--head] [--profile syntax-only|fast|full] [--max-indexed-files n|--index-all-files] [--cache-dir path|--no-cache]\n","move_path":null},"/Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph/README.md":{"type":"update","unified_diff":"@@ -165,5 +165,8 @@\n ```sh\n-entire graph search --repo . --query \"retry logic for webhook delivery\" --top-k 20 --format agent\n+entire graph search --repo . --query \"retry logic for webhook delivery\" --top-k 20 --format agent --head --profile full --cache-dir /path/to/cache\n ```\n \n+That invocation reuses the prepared committed-tree index. Omit `--head` and\n+the cache flags when the agent must inspect dirty working-tree edits instead.\n+\n Search returns ranked, diverse source regions for a task description, fusing several signals:\n","move_path":null}},"status":"completed"}}
