{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T14:44:58.321Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"custom_tool_call","id":"ctc_0bd6d73b974b1fab016a5b916a244c8191b88536e420e3f0e1","status":"completed","call_id":"call_KOTpCyUPxQehSjOGq6JnH5wl","name":"exec","input":"const r = await tools.exec_command({cmd:\"gh auth status && python3 /Users/thomi/.codex/plugins/cache/openai-curated-remote/github/0.1.8-2841cf9749ae/skills/gh-address-comments/scripts/fetch_comments.py --help\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph\",\"yield_time_ms\":30000,\"max_output_tokens\":20000,\"sandbox_permissions\":\"require_escalated\",\"justification\":\"May I confirm GitHub authentication and inspect the thread-aware review fetcher before reading PR #43’s unresolved inline feedback?\",\"prefix_rule\":[\"gh\",\"auth\",\"status\"]}); text(r.output);\n","internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f756f-5147-7222-9084-187ed68d3651"}}}
{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T14:45:04.974Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"custom_tool_call_output","id":"ctco_019f75b0-214e-7a70-acc3-cf0fa67cda76","call_id":"call_KOTpCyUPxQehSjOGq6JnH5wl","output":[{"type":"input_text","text":"Script completed\nWall time 6.6 seconds\nOutput:\n"},{"type":"input_text","text":"github.com\n  ✓ Logged in to github.com account ashtom (/Users/thomi/.config/gh/hosts.yml)\n  - Active account: true\n  - Git operations protocol: https\n  - Token: gho_************************************\n  - Token scopes: 'gist', 'read:org', 'repo', 'workflow'\n{\n  \"pull_request\": {\n    \"number\": 43,\n    \"url\": \"https://github.com/entireio/entire-graph/pull/43\",\n    \"title\": \"Improve agent retrieval and focused graph navigation\",\n    \"state\": \"OPEN\",\n    \"owner\": \"entireio\",\n    \"repo\": \"entire-graph\"\n  },\n  \"conversation_comments\": [],\n  \"reviews\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"PRR_kwDOSqVa0c8AAAABGXDNMg\",\n      \"state\": \"COMMENTED\",\n      \"body\": \"<!-- BUGBOT_REVIEW -->\\nCursor Bugbot has reviewed your changes and found 1 potential issue.\\n\\n\\n\\n<!-- BUGBOT_FIX_ALL -->\\n<a href=\\\"https://cursor.com/open?REDACTED\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\"><picture><source media=\\\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\\\" srcset=\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\\\"><source media=\\\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\\\" srcset=\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-light.png\\\"><img alt=\\\"Fix All in Cursor\\\" width=\\\"115\\\" height=\\\"28\\\" src=\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\\\"></picture></a>\\n<!-- /BUGBOT_FIX_ALL -->\\n\\n<!-- BUGBOT_AUTOFIX_REVIEW_FOOTNOTE_BEGIN -->\\n<sup>\\u274c Bugbot Autofix is OFF. To automatically fix reported issues with cloud agents, enable autofix in the [Cursor dashboard](https://www.cursor.com/dashboard/bugbot).</sup>\\n<!-- BUGBOT_AUTOFIX_REVIEW_FOOTNOTE_END -->\\n\\nWant fixes drafted automatically? **Bugbot Autofix** can create code changes for findings. A team admin can enable Autofix in the [Cursor dashboard](https://www.cursor.com/dashboard/bugbot/installation/1441364).\\n\\n_Comment `@cursor review` or `bugbot run` to trigger another review on this PR_\\n\\n\\n<sup>Reviewed by [Cursor Bugbot](https://cursor.com/bugbot) for commit af44ca236d8abc12043b3d3fa6f33e7e2f5ef4ee. Configure [here](https://www.cursor.com/dashboard/bugbot).</sup>\",\n      \"submittedAt\": \"2026-07-17T10:28:25Z\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"cursor\"\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"review_threads\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"PRRT_kwDOSqVa0c6Ru9PH\",\n      \"isResolved\": false,\n      \"isOutdated\": false,\n      \"path\": \"internal/sem/search_test.go\",\n      \"line\": 180,\n      \"diffSide\": \"RIGHT\",\n      \"startLine\": 180,\n      \"startDiffSide\": null,\n      \"originalLine\": 147,\n      \"originalStartLine\": null,\n      \"resolvedBy\": null,\n      \"comments\": {\n        \"nodes\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"PRRC_kwDOSqVa0c7WuCue\",\n            \"body\": \"### Focused-region test never runs\\n\\n**Medium Severity**\\n\\n<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->\\n`TestSearchRepositoryUsesFocusedDefaultRegions` was inserted inside the raw string fixture of `TestSearchRepositoryPreservesDistinctRegionsInOneFile`, so it is never registered or executed as a Go test. The intended coverage for the new 80-line default never runs, and that other test\\u2019s `timing/wheel.go` fixture is polluted with unrelated source text.\\n<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->\\n\\n<!-- BUGBOT_BUG_ID: e9a0ea51-2f9e-483b-8a43-29e5f139cf9f -->\\n\\n<!-- LOCATIONS START\\ninternal/sem/search_test.go#L116-L147\\ninternal/sem/search_test.go#L109-L157\\nLOCATIONS END -->\\n<details>\\n<summary>Additional Locations (1)</summary>\\n\\n- [`internal/sem/search_test.go#L109-L157`](https://github.com/entireio/entire-graph/blob/af44ca236d8abc12043b3d3fa6f33e7e2f5ef4ee/internal/sem/search_test.go#L109-L157)\\n\\n</details>\\n\\n<div><a href=\\\"https://cursor.com/open?REDACTED\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\"><picture><source media=\\\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\\\" srcset=\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\\\"><source media=\\\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\\\" srcset=\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-light.png\\\"><img alt=\\\"Fix in Cursor\\\" width=\\\"115\\\" height=\\\"28\\\" src=\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\\\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https://cursor.com/agents?REDACTED\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\"><picture><source media=\\\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\\\" srcset=\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-dark.png\\\"><source media=\\\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\\\" srcset=\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-light.png\\\"><img alt=\\\"Fix in Web\\\" width=\\\"99\\\" height=\\\"28\\\" src=\\\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-dark.png\\\"></picture></a></div>\\n\\n\\n<sup>Reviewed by [Cursor Bugbot](https://cursor.com/bugbot) for commit af44ca236d8abc12043b3d3fa6f33e7e2f5ef4ee. Configure [here](https://www.cursor.com/dashboard/bugbot).</sup>\\n\",\n            \"createdAt\": \"2026-07-17T10:28:25Z\",\n            \"updatedAt\": \"2026-07-17T10:28:25Z\",\n            \"author\": {\n              \"login\": \"cursor\"\n            }\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n"}],"internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f756f-5147-7222-9084-187ed68d3651"}}}
