{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T15:22:00.611Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"custom_tool_call_output","id":"ctco_019f75d1-f023-7123-a3cf-e1d085f45ce2","call_id":"call_s5OTPBBs27Wj9eNtdjupjrLx","output":[{"type":"input_text","text":"Script completed\nWall time 4.1 seconds\nOutput:\n"},{"type":"input_text","text":"{\"chunk_id\":\"ef0e08\",\"wall_time_seconds\":3.930999667,\"exit_code\":0,\"original_token_count\":447,\"output\":\"✓ codex/graph-agentic-repair-pilot CI entirehq/brain-bench#34 · 29649314089\\nTriggered via pull_request about 16 minutes ago\\n\\nJOBS\\n✓ regression-gate in 16m0s (ID 88092798669)\\n  ✓ Set up job\\n  ✓ Run actions/checkout@v4\\n  ✓ Run actions/setup-python@v5\\n  ✓ Run actions/setup-go@v5\\n  ✓ Compile all eval tools\\n  ✓ Install test runner\\n  ✓ Install system test dependencies\\n  ✓ Frozen Graph V7 evidence verifies\\n  ✓ Full benchmark and protocol test suite\\n  ✓ CORE-Bench redaction provenance verifies\\n  ✓ Significance report is up to date (no drift)\\n  ✓ Post Run actions/setup-go@v5\\n  ✓ Post Run actions/setup-python@v5\\n  ✓ Post Run actions/checkout@v4\\n  ✓ Complete job\\n\\nANNOTATIONS\\n! Node.js 20 is deprecated. The following actions target Node.js 20 but are being forced to run on Node.js 24: actions/checkout@v4, actions/setup-go@v5, actions/setup-python@v5. For more information see: https://github.blog/changelog/2025-09-19-deprecation-of-node-20-on-github-actions-runners/\\nregression-gate: .github#2\\n\\n! The following taps are not trusted:\\n  aws/tap\\n\\nHomebrew is currently ignoring formulae, casks and commands from these taps because tap trust is required.\\nUntap them with:\\n  brew untap aws/tap\\nTrust specific formulae, casks and commands with:\\n  brew trust --formula <user>/<tap>/<formula>\\n  brew trust --cask <user>/<tap>/<cask>\\n  brew trust --command <user>/<tap>/<command>\\nWhole-tap trust is broader and includes all current and future formulae,\\ncasks and commands from the listed taps. Trust whole taps with:\\n  brew trust aws/tap\\nTo disable trust checks:\\n  export HOMEBREW_NO_REQUIRE_TAP_TRUST=1\\nThis is not recommended and will be removed in a later release.\\nFor more information, see:\\n  https://docs.brew.sh/Tap-Trust\\n\\nregression-gate: .github#11\\n\\n\"}"}],"internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f756f-5147-7222-9084-187ed68d3651"}}}
