{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T15:25:00.130Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"agent_message","message":"The known product and benchmark flaws are fixed, committed, pushed, and green.\n\n- [Entire Graph PR #43](https://github.com/entireio/entire-graph/pull/43), head `2c54486`: durable preindexing, cache provenance, bounded retrieval, mirror deduplication, corrected call graphs, and improved neighborhoods. All 7 platform checks pass.\n- [Brain-Bench draft PR #34](https://github.com/entirehq/brain-bench/pull/34), head `bcb60c7`: honest preindexed protocol with setup excluded, serial execution, exact product isolation, cache-hit enforcement, and fail-closed evidence handling.\n- Brain-Bench CI: **2,370 passed, 6 skipped**; frozen V7 evidence, redaction provenance, and significance-drift checks all pass.\n- Both worktrees are clean and exactly synchronized with GitHub.\n\nPrepared-index deterministic replay:\n\n| Repository | Index setup, excluded | Search | Neighborhood |\n|---|---:|---:|---:|\n| Chi | 0.854s | 24ms | 33ms |\n| Zod | 5.418s | 62ms | 63ms |\n| Click | 3.090s | 57ms | 94ms |\n\nThese are product-validation measurements, not yet proof against CBM and file tools. The earlier paid smoke remains diagnostic because its pipeline included indexing, degraded CBM, asymmetric work, and contention.\n\nThe engineering and evaluation blockers are now removed. The remaining step is a fresh, outcome-blind predefined slice with frozen Graph/CBM/agent heads, prospective preregistration, and repeated paired attempts. I have deliberately not incurred that paid agent spend without fresh authorization. Once authorized, it can run under the corrected protocol; any loss will remain actionable product work rather than being explained away.\n\n::git-stage{cwd=\"/Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph\"}\n::git-commit{cwd=\"/Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph\"}\n::git-push{cwd=\"/Users/thomi/Projects/entire-graph\" branch=\"codex/improve-search-retrieval\"}\n::git-stage{cwd=\"/private/tmp/brain-bench-graph-agentic-pilot\"}\n::git-commit{cwd=\"/private/tmp/brain-bench-graph-agentic-pilot\"}\n::git-push{cwd=\"/private/tmp/brain-bench-graph-agentic-pilot\" branch=\"codex/graph-agentic-repair-pilot\"}","phase":"final_answer","memory_citation":null}}
